# Client environment variables (Vite). Optional — the server URL is auto-detected at runtime:
#   • served from localhost            → http://localhost:3001 (local server)
#   • served from anywhere else (prod) → the deployed Heroku server
#
# Only set this to OVERRIDE that, e.g. to point local dev at the deployed server (or a staging one).
# Copy to `.env` for a local override; in production it's not needed.
# VITE_SERVER_URL=https://football-server-3a8e8a32d792.herokuapp.com
